From: Chao Fu <B44548@freescale.com>
Date: Fri, 24 Oct 2014 15:01:23 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 040/128] arm:dts:ls1021aqds: reduce the frequency for dspi
 flash

Dspi flash is at45db021d on ls1021aqds board.
Reduce its frequency to improve the data transfer stability.

Signed-off-by: Chao Fu <B44548@freescale.com>
Change-Id: If4e4d03d52fc28dea2dca3e6c6872024d3d1229a
Reviewed-on: http://git.am.freescale.net:8181/21973
Tested-by: Review Code-CDREVIEW <CDREVIEW@freescale.com>
Reviewed-by: Zhengxiong Jin <Jason.Jin@freescale.com>
[Xulin: Original patch taken from
QorIQ-SDK-V1.7-SOURCE-20141218-yocto_RDS_20150206.iso]
Signed-off-by: Xulin Sun <xulin.sun@windriver.com>
---
 arch/arm/boot/dts/ls1021a-qds.dts |    2 +-
 1 files changed, 1 insertions(+), 1 deletions(-)

diff --git a/arch/arm/boot/dts/ls1021a-qds.dts b/arch/arm/boot/dts/ls1021a-qds.dts
index 3c54e1b..29aa7af 100644
--- a/arch/arm/boot/dts/ls1021a-qds.dts
+++ b/arch/arm/boot/dts/ls1021a-qds.dts
@@ -114,7 +114,7 @@
 		compatible = "atmel,at45db021d", "atmel,at45", "atmel,dataflash";
 		#address-cells = <1>;
 		#size-cells = <1>;
-		spi-max-frequency = <16000000>;
+		spi-max-frequency = <3000000>;
 		spi-cpol;
 		spi-cpha;
 		reg = <0>;
